{"tid":1963774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE回歸僅三天 專輯銷量突破10萬","createTime":"2020-04-08T10:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T05:36:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1f1a32768b9aa81086b66c49555cbd4d676d1a","tid":1963774,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"(G)I-DLE回歸僅三天 專輯銷量就突破10萬！自身最高記錄<br />\n<br />\n根據8日下午5時30分為準的實時唱片銷量統計網站Hanteo Chart統計結果顯示，(G)I-DLE在6日發行的迷你3輯《I trust》在發售第三天當天累計銷量突破了10萬張，這已經超過了(G)I-DLE自身最高首周銷量紀錄。不僅在韓國國內，在全世界(G)I-DLE也展現了強大的人氣，主打曲《Oh my god》摘得53個地區的iTune Top Album榜單一位。特別是在美國iTunes Pop Album榜單、K-POP Album榜單、K-POP Song榜單上均位列第一，讓人切實感受到了火熱的全球人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HEZKVgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHEZKVgE.png&h=fb88d6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據了解中輸佔80%"},{"pid":"c729d3e3f20a933e8a57dd7185b1f210866d7d8a","tid":1963774,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"10萬炸下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f270ca254763ed0984e2b5106d7e16758879913","tid":1963774,"uid":141656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"輸佔80%？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚玩啦伍寶"},{"pid":"925159ddfff3c612b72369e6afb257d2f0ccb255","tid":1963774,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f270ca254763ed0984e2b5106d7e16758879913","tid":1963774,"uid":141656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"輸佔80%？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚玩啦伍寶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"~78000隻"},{"pid":"9503ae113a91959bbf1c6c9da06893ec7b4e1011","tid":1963774,"uid":134171,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"gidle升到同  blackpink 